<br>
As for the possible fading memories nerf, if they did that I agree that Bards would really be crippled. While we do have a lot of versatility besides fading memories, but we are so underpowered in every single area. To me fading memories has been the great equalizer. Yes, that monk can do 230+ dps and he can FD, mend, hold aggro if he wants and lull with zero resists... but we get fading memories. I honestly feel that its very balanced, if anything I think we ought to be talking about an upgraded fading memories aa from the new expansion that works on see invis mobs. Monks still do 99.9% of all pulling in my guild and most others. If that doesn't show that fading memories isn't that big a deal then I don't know what does.<br>
